      • pageSize

        public static Compute.SubnetworkListOption pageSize(long pageSize)
        Returns an option to specify the maximum number of subnetworks returned per page. pageSize must be between 0 and 500 (inclusive). If not specified 500 is used.

      • pageToken

        public static Compute.SubnetworkListOption pageToken(String pageToken)
        Returns an option to specify the page token from which to start listing subnetworks.

      • fields

        public static Compute.SubnetworkListOption fields(Compute.SubnetworkField... fields)
        Returns an option to specify the subnetwork's fields to be returned by the RPC call. If this option is not provided, all subnetwork's fields are returned. SubnetworListkOption.fields can be used to specify only the fields of interest. SubnetworkInfo.subnetworkId() is always returned, even if not specified.
